Please complete the following exercises and address the following 
questions. Limit your response to a maximum of five pages.

<ol>
<li>What did you learn about yourself from comparing your responses on the 
self-assessment exercise with the characteristics of leaders provided in the sealed envelope?
<li>What further insights did you gain from reviewing the observations of 
your professional colleagues with respect to the degree to which the 
characteristics of leaders were descriptive of you?
<li>Provide examples of personal or professional activities you have 
engaged in during the past two years which you feel exemplify at least 
four of the ten characteristics of leaders.
<li>Tell us what professional literature you have found particularly 
intriguing or exciting during the last six months; describe as well what 
learning experience of a non-professional nature has recently had a 
significant impact on you.
<li>Describe your vision of a learning environment that you find 
personally compelling.
<li>What motivates you to want to participate in the Quality Leadership 
Institute?
<li>How do you see yourself applying what you might learn from such 
participation in an education setting?
<li>Provide any additional statement you wish to make regarding your 
application to the QLI.
</ol>

